PN,31401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775815515
OL,3,CUS-Iran ceasefire deal originally
OL,4,Cincluded Lebanon, sources tell ITV News
OL,6,FThe Iranian and Pakistani delegations
OL,7,Fended negotiations about a ceasefire
OL,8,Fin the Middle East with the clear
OL,9,Funderstanding that the United States
OL,10,Fbelieved the agreement extended to
OL,11,FLebanon, according to a diplomatic
OL,12,Fsource familiar with the frantic final
OL,13,Fhours before a deal was announced.
OL,15,FTheir account appears to contradict
OL,16,Fclaims by the White House on Wednesday
OL,17,Fthat "Lebanon is not part of the
OL,18,Fceasefire."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
