PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775815515
OL,3,CUS-Iran ceasefire deal originally
OL,4,Cincluded Lebanon, sources tell ITV News
OL,6,FTalks involving President Donald
OL,7,FTrump's negotiators, Steve Witkoff and
OL,8,FJared Kushner, stretched beyond 11pm
OL,9,FLondon time on Tuesday as officials
OL,10,Ftried to force a breakthrough,
OL,11,Faccording to an account of the
OL,12,Fnegotiations based on conversations
OL,13,Fwith officials from several countries
OL,14,Fwho have spoken to ITV News.
OL,16,FOn the Iranian side, Foreign Minister
OL,17,FAbbas Araghchi led the discussions,
OL,18,Falongside Pakistan's army chief
OL,19,FGeneral Asim Munir and Turkey's
OL,20,FForeign Minister Hakan Fidan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775815515
OL,3,CUS-Iran ceasefire deal originally
OL,4,Cincluded Lebanon, sources tell ITV News
OL,6,FMessages were relayed between
OL,7,FWashington and Tehran through a
OL,8,Fcomplex diplomatic chain running via
OL,9,FDoha, Ankara and Islamabad. Israel was
OL,10,Fnot directly involved.
OL,12,FSources briefed on the talks told ITV
OL,13,FNews that negotiators ended their
OL,14,Ffinal call at around 11.15pm.
OL,16,FMinutes later, at 11.32pm, President
OL,17,FTrump announced that a two-week
OL,18,Fceasefire would begin immediately.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775815515
OL,3,CUS-Iran ceasefire deal originally
OL,4,Cincluded Lebanon, sources tell ITV News
OL,6,FBut while the statement was presented
OL,7,Fas a breakthrough, the events that
OL,8,Ffollowed confirm a far less settled
OL,9,Fpicture.
OL,11,FAlthough other national delegations
OL,12,Finvolved in the talks had been left
OL,13,Fwith the impression that the ceasefire
OL,14,Fextended to Lebanon, that
OL,15,Finterpretation has been rejected by
OL,16,FWashington ` and undermined on the
OL,17,Fground, where Israeli strikes
OL,18,Fcontinued.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775815515
OL,3,CUS-Iran ceasefire deal originally
OL,4,Cincluded Lebanon, sources tell ITV News
OL,6,FDuring an interview with PBS on
OL,7,FWednesday, Donald Trump said Lebanon
OL,8,Fhad not been included "because of
OL,9,FHezbollah", adding that the attacks by
OL,10,Fthe IDF, in which hundreds were
OL,11,Fkilled, were a "separate skirmish".
OL,13,FLast night, Vice President JD Vance,
OL,14,Fwho will lead the US team in this
OL,15,Fweekend's talks with Iran in Pakistan,
OL,16,Fsaid: "I think this comes from a
OL,17,Flegitimate misunderstanding. I think
OL,18,Fthe Iranians thought that the
OL,19,Fceasefire included Lebanon, and it
OL,20,Fjust didn't."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775815515
OL,3,CUS-Iran ceasefire deal originally
OL,4,Cincluded Lebanon, sources tell ITV News
OL,6,FPakistan's reading of the US position
OL,7,Fcarries particular weight, given
OL,8,FGeneral Munir's close relationship
OL,9,Fwith Trump ` and raises questions
OL,10,Fabout how such a fundamental
OL,11,Fdivergence in understanding emerged at
OL,12,Fthe point of agreement.
OL,14,FA ceasefire in Lebanon was thought to
OL,15,Fbe one of few firm details agreed by
OL,16,Fboth sides, according to diplomatic
OL,17,Fsources. Mediators had encouraged Iran
OL,18,Fto make only vague proposals, leaving
OL,19,Fspecifics to be fleshed out at the
OL,20,Fpeace talks in Islamabad later this
OL,21,Fweek.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775815515
OL,3,CUS-Iran ceasefire deal originally
OL,4,Cincluded Lebanon, sources tell ITV News
OL,6,FTehran's proposal of a fee on vessels
OL,7,Fpassing through the Strait of Hormuz -
OL,8,Fdescribed by some negotiators as a
OL,9,F"toll booth" for global shipping - was
OL,10,Fdeferred, along with other contentious
OL,11,Fissues.
OL,13,FThere is also concern among diplomats
OL,14,Fthat any commitments made by Iran's
OL,15,Fdelegation may ultimately require
OL,16,Fapproval from the Islamic
OL,17,FRevolutionary Guard Corps,
OL,18,Fcomplicating implementation.
OL,20,FBehind the scenes, the diplomatic
OL,21,Feffort had been vast.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
