OL,3,CUS-Iran ceasefire deal originally
OL,4,Cincluded Lebanon, sources tell ITV News
OL,6,FA Turkish diplomatic source said
OL,7,FForeign Minister Hakan Fidan held more
OL,8,Fthan 150 calls in the days leading up
OL,9,Fto the agreement, including around 50
OL,10,Ffocused solely on shaping the format
OL,11,Fof talks in Islamabad.
