PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775815515
OL,3,CUS-Iran ceasefire deal originally
OL,4,Cincluded Lebanon, sources tell ITV News
OL,6,FAs regional tensions escalated, Ankara
OL,7,Falso warned Tehran that potential
OL,8,Ftargets had been identified by other
OL,9,FMiddle Eastern states as part of a
OL,10,Fparallel push to contain the conflict.
OL,12,FThose concerns had been building for
OL,13,Fweeks. On March 18, foreign ministers
OL,14,Ffrom Turkey, Pakistan, and several
OL,15,FGulf states - including Saudi Arabia
OL,16,Fand Qatar - met in Riyadh to
OL,17,Fcoordinate their response.
OL,19,FWith the Eid holiday approaching, they
OL,20,Fagreed that avoiding full-scale war
OL,21,Fmust be the priority.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
