PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775815515
OL,3,CUS-Iran ceasefire deal originally
OL,4,Cincluded Lebanon, sources tell ITV News
OL,6,FSaudi Arabia's foreign minister told
OL,7,Fme at the time that the Kingdom's
OL,8,Fpatience was "not unlimited", urging
OL,9,FIran to "recalculate" ` while
OL,10,Fexpressing doubt that its leadership
OL,11,Fwould do so.
OL,13,FGulf states chose not to retaliate.
OL,15,FBut the deal agreed to on Tuesday
OL,16,Fleaves Lebanon emerging as the deal's
OL,17,Fmost immediate and dangerous fault
OL,18,Fline.
